---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import Cta from '../../../components/Cta.astro';
import { articleSchema, breadcrumbSchema } from '../../../lib/schema';
const path = '/frequency/code/';
const title = 'The Frequency Code™: What It Is & How It’s Built';
const description = 'The Frequency Code™ is the personalized report at the center of Archangel Frequencies — what it contains, how it is built from your birthdate, and how it differs from the free tools.';
const crumbs = [
  { name: 'Home', href: '/' },
  { name: 'Frequency', href: '/frequency/' },
  { name: 'The Frequency Code™', href: path },
];
const schema = [articleSchema({ title, description, path }), breadcrumbSchema(crumbs)];
---
<Base title={title} description={description} schema={schema}>
  <div class="article">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={crumbs} />
    <header class="hero"><p class="eyebrow">Signature Methodology</p><h1>The Frequency Code™</h1></header>
    <p>The Frequency Code™ is the personalized report every free tool on this site points toward. Where an angel-number page reads one sequence and a calculator reveals one number, the Frequency Code™ takes every number tied to your birthdate — your angel number, your life path, your current personal year — and reads them together, as one signal instead of several separate ones.</p>
    <h2>How It's Built</h2>
    <p>The method is the same three-step system described on our <a href="/methodology/">methodology page</a> — core digit, pattern, reduction — applied across your full set of personal numbers at once rather than one page at a time, then cross-referenced against the <a href="/frequency/248/">248 Frequency™</a>: which of the three core themes (balance, foundation, return) your numbers keep circling back to. A single free angel-number page can tell you what 444 means in general. The Frequency Code™ tells you what 444 means for someone whose life path is a 7 and whose personal year is a 2 — the combination is specific to you, not a lookup.</p>
    <h2>What's Inside</h2>
    <p>The report runs 26 pages and covers the same categories as the free angel-number pages — spiritual meaning, love, money and career, twin flame, biblical reading — but written for your specific numbers rather than one sequence in isolation, plus a forward-looking section the free content can't offer without your birthdate: where the next twelve months are pointed, and the specific place your energy tends to leak when the pattern goes unread.</p>
    <h2>How It's Different From the Free Tools</h2>
    <p>The calculators on this site are free and stay free — the angel number calculator, life path calculator, personal year calculator, and mirror hour decoder all give you a real number and a real reading, no email required. The Frequency Code™ is the next layer: instead of one number, the full set, read as one pattern. Most people start with a calculator, recognize themselves in it, and come back for the Frequency Code™ when they want the whole picture rather than one piece of it.</p>
    <p>The report is $27, one time, no subscription. Start with the free <a href="/angel-numbers/calculator/">angel number calculator</a> first if you haven't — it takes fifteen seconds and shows you whether the system resonates before you spend anything.</p>
    <Cta heading="Get your Frequency Code™" line="Twenty-six pages, built from your numbers alone." />
  </div>
</Base>
